            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-31907291fa4b4d31-2ab9e2 twpub-31907291fa4b4d31-65abb9 twpub-31907291fa4b4d31-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"transnote\"><br>\n<br>\nTRANSCRIBER’S NOTE: In the printed version of this text, all apostrophes for contractions such as “can’t”, “wouldn’t” and “he’d” were omitted, to read as “cant”, “wouldnt”, and “hed”. This etext edition restores the omitted apostrophes.<br>\n<br>\n<br></p></div>"
